951
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

952
00:45:29,000 --> 00:45:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali što su tome, recimo, ljudi su se uvijek,

953
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad su došli stroje, razbijali su strojeve.

954
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

955
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,000
