976
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji to tvrde.

977
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači imamo Jeffrey Hinton, pre koji je dobro Nobelo nagradu.

978
00:46:58,000 --> 00:47:01,000
