980
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Još nije bio Nobelovac.

981
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zanimljivo nato, to je dobro Nobelo nagradu.

982
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Al ne zahvaliči meni.

983
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je, veli sada, da je pitanje dana kada će meni da inteligencija postati svjesna.

984
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kada će s nama zavladati.

985
00:47:22,000 --> 00:47:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vaše misljenje, to su ti.

986
00:47:24,000 --> 00:47:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ovako, sve ovako.

987
00:47:26,000 --> 00:47:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pitam njega, Rama, kad ga je uvijek zovem.

988
00:47:31,000 --> 00:47:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li ćeš mijeniti silu ako će čovječanstvo samo sebe ugrožiti.

989
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] On mi odgovara ovak.

990
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovisi kak me programirate.

991
00:47:41,000 --> 00:47:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mi date naredbu da ja u slučaju ugroženosti čovječanstva moram silom uspostaviti.

992
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:49,000
