993
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na tome, još vijek i u našim rukama.

994
00:47:51,000 --> 00:47:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, naravno, tu i postoji kontrargument koji ovaj navodi Utkovski.

995
00:47:56,000 --> 00:48:02,000
