1037
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koja se koristi u karcinomu.

1038
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod operacija karcinoma prostate.

1039
00:50:57,000 --> 00:50:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koje reže.

1040
00:50:58,000 --> 00:50:59,000
