1047
00:51:17,000 --> 00:51:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mlada prekrasna lijepa.

1048
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naših roditelja.

1049
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rodila se gore.

1050
00:51:21,000 --> 00:51:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ima nekakav prvi stadin karcinoma na maternici.

1051
00:51:26,000 --> 00:51:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] To nije prodalo u otraga, u tijelu itd.

1052
00:51:29,000 --> 00:51:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad to oni su nje rekli gore histerectomije.

1053
00:51:32,000 --> 00:51:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači uklanjanje svega.

1054
00:51:33,000 --> 00:51:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona ne mogli nikad rodit niš.

1055
00:51:35,000 --> 00:51:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je očajna bilo.

1056
00:51:37,000 --> 00:51:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam za jednog čovjeka koji je u celju, u bolnici.

1057
00:51:41,000 --> 00:51:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Počeo uvoditi da Vinčeva u platforma operacije.

1058
00:51:44,000 --> 00:51:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne na tome.

1059
00:51:46,000 --> 00:51:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nije ga nazoram.

1060
00:51:47,000 --> 00:51:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mala je dječki bolki rog.

1061
00:51:49,000 --> 00:51:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Reku gledajte.

1062
00:51:50,000 --> 00:51:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Takve se situacije radi.

1063
00:51:52,000 --> 00:51:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li možete, evo, napaviti izriku, pa to operi radi.

1064
00:51:55,000 --> 00:51:58,000
